   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">With the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Adobe Sign Services User Guide</b>, you can find out how <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Adobe Sign for
            Adapter</b> works and how to manage your organization's and your customers' eSignature
         workflows. </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Topic</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
